{
  "texts": [
    "Indeed, out of the range, a specific risk category may be inadequate for the risk scenario, with measures too stringent or too soft to balance competing EU values, like privacy and technological innovation.",
    "In this way, the AIA fails to achieve one of its main objectives: a uniform protection of EU fundamental rights.",
    "We are aware that compulsory numerical values of EU principles and fundamental rights cannot be pre-assigned.",
    "Also, attempts to establish a strict hierarchy among EU fundamental values and rights have so far failed.",
    "39 While acknowledging the importance of these circumstances, we believe that a quantitative method for assessing risk containment measures could help relevant actors make policy decisions and avoid significant imbalances when implementing the AIA."
  ]
}